## combo

## series
| field | as | type | color | axis | style |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 销售额 | 销售额(万元) | bar | #4fc3f7 | left | solid |
| 利润 | 利润(万元) | line | #ff9800 | right | smooth |

## axis x
labelRotate: 45

## axis y
min: 0
max: 200
labelFormatter: "${value}万"
splitLine: true

## axis y2
min: 0
max: 50
labelFormatter: "${value}%"

@interaction "tooltip:shared zoom:inside"
@color "#4fc3f7"